http://www.bedbathandbeyond.com/store/product/squish-collapsible-splatter-shield/1041698020
Stop messy, hot splatters on your stove with this collapsible splatter shield. Use it over hot skillets to catch hot oil and grease before it gets on walls, counters or you. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: This is the square silicone splatter screen from bed bath and beyond. Cook with less mess using this convenient splatter screen. The generous 13 inch size accommodates most frying pans and is high heat resistant. Up to 500 degrees. This bladder screen features unique fold up sides so you can easily check on your dish without removing the entire screen. The fold up side snap closed making it easy to store and takes up less space than other splatter screens and the screen is dishwasher safe. The squish silicone splatter screen available at a bed bath and beyond near you.
